Title: Iron Fortress Mk I
Description:
A small fortress with mainly mark I bots. A lot of mark 1 bots.

Features:
1. Main area - can be accessed from the front entrance or from the roof;
2. Roof - can be accessed from the jump pad in the back;
3. Bottom area - can be accessed from the sides and from the back.

Difficulties:
1 bronze, 1 silver, 1 gold, 1 diamond.

Have fun!
